author: marvin
msg: The language of June 2013 Board Resolution G allows for the Board to
receive notification of a PMC addition from a PMC Chair at any time.
It's only other PMC members who must link to the result of a VOTE
This commit changes the instructions to be compatible with sending the
72-hour NOTICE while the VOTE is underway.
See discussion thread in board@apache archives starting 2013-09-05.
